            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot rustic sausage & butter bean stew</strong></p><p>Drizzle with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and season to taste</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
